title: Episode 29 - Michael Milton Interview (Brink Vault 2010)
itunes:title: Episode 29 - Michael Milton Interview (Brink Vault 2010)
description: The 'vault' is once again opened today as we go back to 2010 and feature our very first Paralympian by chatting with the greatest Australian Winter Paralympics athlete Michael Milton. From the early challenges he had to overcome right through his change into summer sports, it's all covered in this entertaining chat.
